  <summary date="2022-03-09T17:33:45Z" status="Introduced in House">Accountability in Foreign Animal Research Act

This bill prohibits the National Institutes of Health from conducting or supporting research that involves testing on vertebrate animals in China, Cuba, Iran, North Korea, Russia, or other countries determined to be a foreign adversary.</summary>
